properties.Name: DateType
properties.Description:
The type of date:

Dates related to a claim can include:

Ex:
- Filed date
- Received date
- Adjusted date
- Paid date
- Arbitration requested date
- Arbitration completed date
- Claim paid date
- Claim denied date

Dates associated with an Insurance Policy can include:

Ex:
- Effective Date
- Expiration Date
- Exclusions Change Date
- Binder Change Date
- Cancellation Date
- Non-Renewal Date
- Renewal Date
- Conversion Date
- Transfer Date
- Donation Date
